redesign, they would

00:29:17.470 --> 00:29:21.420
like to retain some of
that original anarchist

00:29:21.420 --> 00:29:23.390
spirit of Reddit.

00:29:23.390 --> 00:29:27.670
They want to retain some of that
Aaron Swartziness of it, right?

00:29:27.670 --> 00:29:30.490
That I-- that rebel feeling.

00:29:30.490 --> 00:29:32.350
And so even during
the redesign, they

00:29:32.350 --> 00:29:35.560
brought in a bunch of staff
