Reddit today is

00:30:34.570 --> 00:30:36.290
trying to move into the future.

00:30:36.290 --> 00:30:37.750
It would like to be--

00:30:37.750 --> 00:30:40.930
to have its users be a little
less anonymous, I think.

00:30:40.930 --> 00:30:43.990
You have the ability now
to create a profile page.

00:30:43.990 --> 00:30:46.120
